title.label: Actually taking my time to rate this

content.label: Froggy Jump is an entertaining game. It has challenges that are fun to achieve and the method of currency keeps you wanting to progress more in the game. My one warning: remember it's just a game. It's very easy to spend money on this app but when you do it's not that rewarding. Its a good way to waste time, just don't waste your money too.
